quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  4,176,( ae paighambar ) log tum se ( kalalah ke baray mein ) hukum ( khuda ) daryaft karte hain keh do ke khuda kalalah ke baray mein yeh hukum deta hai ke agar koi aisa mard marjaye jis ke aulaad nah ho ( aur nah maa baap ) aur is ke behan ho to is ko bhai ke trke mein se aadha hissa miley ga. aur agar behan marjaye aur is ke aulaad nah ho to is ke tamam maal ka waris bhai hoga aur agar ( marnay walay bhai ki ) do behnain hon to dono ko bhai ke trke mein se do tahai. aur agar bhai aur behan yani mard aur aurtain miley jalay waris hon to mard ka hissa do aurton ke barabar hai. ( yeh ehkaam ) khuda tum se is liye bayan farmata hai ke bhataktay nah phiro. aur khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  5,1,ae imaan walo! apne iqraron ko poora karo. tumahray liye charpaye janwar ( jo charnay walay hain ) halal kar diye gay hain. bajuz un ke jo tumhe parh kar sunaye jatay hain magar ahram ( hajj ) mein shikaar ko halal nah janna. khuda jaissa chahta hai hukum deta hai
  5,2,momino! khuda ke naam ki cheezon ki be hurmati nah karna aur nah adab ke mahinay ki aur nah qurbani ke janwaron ki aur nah un janwaron ki ( jo khuda ki Nazar kar diye gay hon aur ) jin ke gulon mein pitay bandhay hon aur nah un logon ki jo izzat ke ghar ( yani beeet allah ) ko ja rahay hon ( aur ) apne perwar-digaar ke fazl aur is ki khushnodi ke tallab-gaar hon aur jab ahram utaar do to ( phir ikhtiyar hai ke ) shikaar karo aur logon ki dushmani is wajah se ke unhon ne tum ko izzat wali masjid se roka tha tumhe is baat par amaada nah kere ke tum un par zayad-ti karne lagu aur ( dekho ) neki aur parhaiz gari ke kamon mein aik dosray ki madadkiya karo aur gunah aur zulm ki baton mein madad nahkiya karo aur khuda se drtay raho. kuch shak nahi ke khuda ka azaab sakht hai
